*Kaqemeex was the main NPC during the [[2014 Midsummer event|2014]] and [[2015 Midsummer event]], where players would solve Riddles given to them by [[Thordur]], for rewards such as the [[half full wine jug]] and the untradeable [[druidic wreath]]. Players could also keep the [[disk of returning]] given to them by Thordur.

